org.jcvi.jillion.trace

Interface Trace

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AbiChromatogram, Chromatogram, FastqRecord, Fragment, Phd, ScfChromatogram, SffFlowgram, ZtrChromatogram
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicChromatogram, CommentedParsedFastqRecord, DefaultFragment, ParsedFastqRecord, ScfChromatogramImpl, ZTRChromatogramImpl

    public interface Trace
    A Trace is an abstraction of a piece of genomic sequence data that has been sequenced on some kind of sequencing machine.
    Author:
    dkatzel
